{"tid":2236190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"司機堵路罪成 裁判官鄭念慈不信撞車之說 判阻嚇刑罰囚六周","createTime":"2020-10-09T09:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T01:23:40.000Z","uid":56115,"like":12,"dislike":181,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"9108d6e7e678a67706663f5d132e4b7566eb6846","tid":2236190,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"去年8.5大三罷當日，中年商人被指將平治房車停泊在九龍城迴旋處慢線「堵路」，被控在公眾地方造成阻礙罪。商人辯稱當時遭另一車輛碰撞，對方不顧而去，故報警停車等候警察到場。惟裁判官鄭念慈不接納被告撞車之說，認為只是煙幕以掩飾堵路真相，裁定罪成，並指堵路行為嚴重影響公眾秩序，對上班市民造成不便，必須判處阻嚇性刑罰，以防患於未然，遂判監六星期。"},{"pid":"e2ca84f6ec2527f6813c789163f7f1975971f626","tid":2236190,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=da530130\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI%2F&h=a4e26c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI/</a>"},{"pid":"b8f9ea5c79e564e830fdc4ae4a25fd768889d8d4","tid":2236190,"uid":110043,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"又係le 隻鄭狗"},{"pid":"28f27845f38b06f93045f7482d8e5c76f38deac5","tid":2236190,"uid":56115,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:50:51.000Z","msg":"辯方求情透露，被告從事海產貿易生意，惟收入受疫情影響已大不如前，希望法庭考慮案發當日被告的錯誤決定並無造成長時間交通阻塞，並承諾不會再犯。鄭官聞言反駁：「我唔接納錯誤，我裁定係故意堵路。」"},{"pid":"f29d75690d249607d1373c735cb05539148d926f","tid":2236190,"uid":187664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"狗官"},{"pid":"b1722b97a4782f9689b4c707e7d9ea43a7ef7412","tid":2236190,"uid":49457,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-0